sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant Database
participant GoogleADK
participant AuthService
participant LoadBalancer
participant Server

User->>Frontend: Login Request
Frontend->>AuthService: Validate Credentials
AuthService->>Database: Check Credentials
Database-->>AuthService: Valid Credentials
AuthService-->>Frontend: Auth Token
Frontend-->>User: Login Success

User->>Frontend: Upload CSV/Excel File
Frontend->>Backend: Process File
Backend->>Database: Store Data
Database-->>Backend: Data Stored
Backend-->>Frontend: Success
Frontend-->>User: File Uploaded

User->>Frontend: Request Dashboard
Frontend->>Backend: Get Analytics
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend->>GoogleADK: Get Predictions
GoogleADK-->>Backend: Predictions
Backend-->>Frontend: Analytics
Frontend-->>User: Dashboard

User->>Frontend: Request Report
Frontend->>Backend: Generate Report
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend-->>Frontend: Report
Frontend-->>User: Report

LoadBalancer->>Server: Route Request
Server->>Backend: Process Request
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend-->>Server: Response
Server-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>User: Response

AuthService->>GoogleADK: Validate Token
GoogleADK-->>AuthService: Valid Token
AuthService-->>Frontend: Auth Token
Frontend-->>User: Login Success